  <brief_title>A Cluster Randomized Trial to Improve Weaning and Extubation From Mechanical Ventilation in Community Hospitals</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Cluster Randomized Trial to Improve Weaning and Extubation From Mechanical Ventilation in Community Hospitals</official_title>
